"bob" the word for a small tail, a common nickname in English speaking places and all around a very nice <round> sound - bob. Tigerbob. And there you have it. A tiger thing. My tiger thing. Tigerbob. Tigerbob shared with you. My tiger shared with you. - @grelysian https://t.co/wnYnsCyZTG

but why tiger + bob? Well, firstly, I associated with the term "bob" as endearing definition of a "thing" specifically a "character" of iteration. I found this association from @eBoyArts blockbob @eboyblockbob designs. (I asked permission before adding bob to tiger -bob)ğŸ‘ https://t.co/SLYNJEj1cw
